sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as Browser
    participant Gateway as Gateway API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+ (service-ca)
    participant Backend as odh-dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant BFF as BFF Sidecar<br/>(e.g. gen-ai-ui)<br/>8143/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Upstream as Upstream Service<br/>(e.g. DS Pipeline)<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 1: Standard Dashboard Request
    Browser->>Gateway: GET /api/status<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS 1.2+ (Gateway cert)
    KRBAC->>KRBAC: Validate OIDC Token<br/>Check K8s RBAC<br/>(can list projects?)
    KRBAC->>Backend: Forward HTTP/8080<br/>X-Auth-Request-User header<br/>X-Auth-Request-Groups header
    Backend->>K8sAPI: GET /apis/...<br/>HTTPS/6443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token (user's forwarded token)
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: K8s Resource Response
    Backend-->>KRBAC: JSON Response
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: HTTPS Response
    Gateway-->>Browser: JSON Response

    Note over Browser,BFF: Flow 2: Module Federation BFF Request
    Browser->>Gateway: GET /_mf/gen-ai/api/...<br/>HTTPS/443
    Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward HTTPS/8443<br/>OIDC validation
    KRBAC->>Backend: Forward HTTP/8080<br/>Auth headers injected
    Backend->>BFF: Proxy HTTPS/8143<br/>TLS 1.2+ (shared service cert)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token header
    BFF->>K8sAPI: API call HTTPS/6443<br/>Bearer Token (user or modules SA)
    K8sAPI-->>BFF: Response
    BFF-->>Backend: JSON Response
    Backend-->>KRBAC: Response
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: HTTPS Response
    Gateway-->>Browser: JSON Response

    Note over Browser,Upstream: Flow 3: Service Proxy (e.g. Pipelines, Model Registry)
    Browser->>Gateway: ALL /api/service/pipelines/*<br/>HTTPS/443
    Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward HTTPS/8443<br/>OIDC validation
    KRBAC->>Backend: Forward HTTP/8080<br/>Auth headers injected
    Backend->>Upstream: Proxy HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS 1.2+ (service-ca)<br/>Bearer Token (user's forwarded token)
    Upstream-->>Backend: Service Response
    Backend-->>KRBAC: Response
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: HTTPS Response
    Gateway-->>Browser: JSON Response
